- Redesigned Journey page content and layout to a clean sectioned list with icons.
  File: app/templates/journey.html

- Redesigned Portfolio page with a hero, callout, and project cards.
  File: app/templates/portfolio.html

- Redesigned Certifications page with a hero, callout, and certification card.
  File: app/templates/certifications.html

- Redesigned Contact page into a contact card with email/LinkedIn/GitHub.
  File: app/templates/contact.html

- Overhauled site styling into a DevOps/SRE-friendly design system.
  File: app/static/css/styles.css
  - New color palette, gradients, shadows, typography, and layout primitives.
  - New header/nav styling, cards, badges, and list styles.
  - Updated buttons and project tags to match the new palette.

- Added typography imports for Fraunces + Manrope.
  File: app/templates/base.html

- Improved mobile responsiveness across header, nav, cards, and content.
  File: app/static/css/styles.css

Note: The live deployment on Raspberry Pi may need cache purge or service restart
for changes to appear.
